## Custom Forms

Run:
```sql
SELECT id, name FROM customform WHERE recordtype IN ('journalentry', 'advintercompanyjournalentry') AND isinactive = 'F'
```

| ID | Name | Use |
|----|------|-----|
| <id> | Standard Journal Entry | Default for normal `journalentry` |
| <id> | Standard AICJE | Default for `advintercompanyjournalentry` |

