## Legacy / deprecated accounts (if any)

If your org has retired accounts that should trigger a warning when used in a
new JE, list them here and update `scripts/validate_je.py:LEGACY_ICO_ACCOUNT`
to a `LEGACY_ACCOUNTS` set.

## Where this file is read

- `scripts/validate_je.py` — subsidiary ID validation, custom form fallback
- `scripts/render_preview.py` — pretty-prints names next to IDs

Update this file FIRST when subsidiaries or accounts change in NetSuite.
